short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A helper to start Session by clicking a timer button on your favorite productivity app

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Warning: This extension needs Session app on Mac to be installed. Clicking the timer icon will start Session on Mac (from https://www.stayinsession.com)

This extension helps you start Session by clicking an icon that added to your favorite productivity website.

Current supported websites:
- Todoist (automatically match todoist project with Session category)
- Trello
- Github

URL schemes are documented on https://www.stayinsession.com/learn/session-url-scheme
